Detailed Description

is a StackMsgActiveWaitDispatcher which keeps the Tipd of the transaction for which the dispatcher is instanciated for. Typical transactions are voice calls, and call independent supplementary services.

AbortCause  cause = NotSpecified

Aborts active wait dispatcher only if argument tipd is equal to the tipd of the transaction the acive wait dispatcher is intended for. The AbortCause is set to NotSpecifed.
